data.description: Conveniently located home near Seven Points in Florence, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom has been recently updated and is ready for you. The HVAC is new with new ducts and vents in 2023.  Kitchen updated that includes new stainless steel appliances in April 2023.  Half bath was remodeled October 2023.  Breaker box was updated and service to 200 amp in January 2024.  All new baseboards were added.  New crown molding is being completed.  Pool liner was new in September 2022. All new plugs and switches were added in 2023.  There is a large covered back porch perfect for entertaining as well as a big storage room. All information to be verified by the buyer.  Call today for your today!
